Nothing beats a nice bath after finishing work. And of
course, after this, it's time for drinks at the pub.\I[15]

"Wow... This chick's tits are amazing...♪ Heh, talk about a

(Wow... This chick's boobs are amazing...♪ Heh, talk about a

...\I[15]If you're going to stare at my chest so intently,
would you like to touch them? Ufufu\I[15]

Eeh--!? What are you saying, in such a public place? Young
girls these days are so bold...

Hmm...? A defeated samurai? How rude. If you let down a
topknot, everyone's hair looks like this, doesn't it?

Edo has many fires, so private baths are prohibited except
for the lords and merchants, which is why public baths are
always bustling.

Hey, you shouldn't frolic in the bath. It'll bother other
people, you know.
Ahaha! The bathhouse's bath is so spacious! (Splish splash!)

(Hmm, looking in the mirror, I see more fine lines have
appeared...)
Hey? You've been watching me for a while now, haven't you?
I noticed your gaze. Are you interested in a woman's body?

--In response to Karin's question, the boy's face turned red
as he shook his head, but contrary to his words, his member
was swelling.
少年を誘惑する\c[27]【Ｈイベント】\c[0]
It's Karin. Hello. I've come to take a bath again today.

I'm so sorry about last time! I dirtied your face, big
sister...!

Ahaha, don't worry about it. I was the one who invited
Kisanosuke after all.
Even so... this public bath is always crowded, isn't it?

Yeah. The people of Edo love their baths. Some come three
times a day, and since there aren't many baths around here,
it gets crowded easily.

Kisanosuke is a child of this public bath, right? Your
father and mother are--

...Both my parents died of illness three years ago, so I was
raised by my grandpa and grandma. But then, grandma passed
away last year... Now it's just me and grandpa running this
bathhouse.
...I'm sorry to hear that. That must be tough...

Not really. The bathhouse is a place of relaxation for the
townspeople of Edo. The customers are mostly nice people, so
it's fairly enjoyable.
...? What's wrong? You've suddenly gone quiet.

...No! It's nothing! (Thump-thump... When I look at big
sister's body again, it's so beautiful)
Hm? Could it be... you're captivated by my body?
--! No, that's not it! It's nothing, really!

(Kisanosuke, with his face all red... He's really
cute\I[15])
弥太吉を誘惑する\c[27]【Ｈイベント】\c[0]
Right. See you again then. I'm going to enjoy the bath.

--After bathing and feeling refreshed, Karin took a nap on
the tatami in the resting area before heading home.
Hello, Yatakich! How have you been?

Ah, Karin-neechan--!? You came to the bathhouse again today.
Ehehe, I'm so happy.

The bathhouse is closing early today, isn't it? Usually,
it's open until the fifth hour of the night (8 PM).

Yeah. Today is the once-a-month big cleaning day. We clean
the baths every day after closing, but the big cleaning
includes everything up to the ceiling, so it's tough.

Oh, I see. So you're doing the big cleaning with your
grandfather.

Grandpa has been called to a drinking party at the
association, so he won't be here tonight. That means I end
up having to do the cleaning all by myself...
Is that so? That sounds tough.

If you have time, neechan, I'd really like your help with
the big cleaning...

(Poor Yatakich, having to clean all by himself. What should
I do...)
弥太吉を手伝う\c[27]【Ｈイベント】\c[0]

I'm sorry. I have things to do too... I'll be leaving right
after I take a bath today.

Yay! Mitakichi, have you been well? I came to take a bath
again today.

Welcome, big sister! Thank you for helping me with the big
cleaning the other day.

Ahaha... That was a close call for both of us... We were
supposed to clean, but ended up dirtying the bathtub and
floor...

I'm sorry. I get so excited when you're with me... I won't
be able to hold back today either...
~~~~! (Wow... His dick is already rock hard...\I[15])

After the bathhouse closes for the day... Can I... love you
lots again, big sister?
うん、いいよ\I[15]\c[10]【銭湯エンド】\c[0]
Sorry, Mitakichi. I have other things to do today.

Really? Aww, that's too bad... I'll be waiting for you
forever, so please come again, big sister.

(Phew... Soaking in the bath at the public bathhouse is the
best...♪)

--Health and skill power have been \c[24]fully
restored\c[0]!
